Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,……{防止内封bug}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但真是太突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是身體不舒服跟我們說一聲就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定是媽媽妳太忙 怕打攪妳才不說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳應該很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奶奶就是這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黛西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳是在責怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才沒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是覺得奶奶一定想多看看妳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也一定想妳多陪陪她而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.05,0:02:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為奶奶她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對妳是那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是因為奶奶的媽媽很早就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}信件？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是妳奶奶的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去世後給妳奶奶寄的信件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去世後還能寄信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}似乎委託了人偶幫忙代筆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使自己去世了 也會每年生日寄一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有會寫信的洋娃娃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳誤會了 是以前為失明的妻子發明打字機的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把打字機器命名為自動手記人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那以後 從事代筆的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都會被稱呼為人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}代筆？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幫忙寫信的意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:04:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在以前會讀書寫字的人還很少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但後來 會寫字的人多了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}電話也開始普及
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寄信的人也開始減少後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這份工作應該已經消失不見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}需要寫些特別的信件 或者寫不好的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都會找人偶幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些信件 妳奶奶保管得非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}病人都等著妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走了 黛西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要再待一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}葬禮一結束 人全都走了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奶奶一定會很傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黛西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽妳就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟妳總把工作看得比家庭重要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不單只妳奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有妳 我都看得很重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走吧 我送妳到車站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黛西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}工作結束後我們會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我又對媽媽說難聽的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我明明清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽的工作有多辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安 祝妳8歲生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或許妳會有很多不開心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或許妳會有太多事情要做而感到力不從心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是不要認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或許妳會有寂寞想哭的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但請不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽一直愛著妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安 祝妳10歲生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想必妳已經長高許多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是妳依舊喜歡看書跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}應該沒再玩猜謎和抓蟲子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}祝妳18歲生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳已經是一個端莊的淑女了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有沒有遇到喜歡的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然不能幫妳解決戀愛的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但既然是妳看中的 就一定是個好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生日快樂 安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳已經活過20年了 真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使長大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偶爾發下牢騷也是不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果妳感到不知所措 記住有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:08:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會一直一直守護妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每年的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都會收到這樣的信件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太外婆一定非常關心我奶奶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是剪報？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寫下這些信件的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}似乎是當時非常出名的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有時候會寫寫公主殿下的情書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有時候受歌姬委託寫寫新歌劇的歌詞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}更有時候 還會給知名劇作家代筆舞臺劇本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:10:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個來自萊頓某郵局的人偶即使如此風光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自從18歲辭職離開郵局後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}便再也沒看到關於她的報道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而這個人偶的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:27.64,title,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\t(0,8500,\fs54)\move(960,500,960,505)\t(5863,9000,\alphaA8)\t(9000,11680,0.3,\alphaFF)\b0}薇爾莉特·伊芙嘉登
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在東北戰地撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還沒取名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 給我打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別動粗 她還這麼小
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吉爾 她可不是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是用來戰鬥的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我來取名字可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳叫薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}長大後 妳一定會變成像妳名字一樣的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳不是道具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳會成為像妳名字一樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特·伊芙嘉登
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請上前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本年度海之讚歌的起草者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}向本年度海之女神依瑪·費列齊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}交付了讚歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海之讚歌 實在太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是啊 沒有白費心血
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不同於一般的信件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大海無邊無際廣闊無垠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}許多水生生物以此為家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不僅資源豐富而且充滿魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她不像人那樣有功績 立場或人格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想出如何稱讚她費了我好多心機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這…不過 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 那明年我來寫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海之讚歌可是點名寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天就開始寫一大堆驚艷世人的信件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你等著我被點名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對吧 薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的 我們都等著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特·伊芙嘉登
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}市長好 夫人好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特 這是萊頓市長和他的夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若客有所求 則使命必達
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:15:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是自動手記人偶服務的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特·伊芙嘉登
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真美啊 真的像人偶一般
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我經常聽說妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今年妳會為傳統的大海感謝日而書寫讚歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實是我推薦的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳曾經寫過的公開情書
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}裡面的弗呂格爾王國 達米安國王的宣誓書
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個寫得實在太優美了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}優美得就像妳一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}加冕儀式的宣誓書
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是把達米安國王的理想和志向寫成文字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然您用優美來形容我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那份宣誓書
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我認為和我自身是毫無關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請海涵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特 也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是說 我在誇獎妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為妳作為人偶 成績非常優異
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而過去作為軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也拯救了萊頓夏福特利這座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這座城市不是我拯救的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這要歸功於上場作戰的士兵們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 這場戰鬥也同時奪走了大量生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我並非是一個值得誇獎的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要炒麵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偶爾換換口味嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:17:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾莉卡女士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}氣色不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}社長 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}劇作家助手的工作已經上手了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是之前薇爾莉特代過筆的那個老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前看戲的時候 把艾莉卡介紹給了他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死求百賴才把我收下當徒弟的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老師他每天都寫完改改完寫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把原稿打出來都會把我累死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我很受用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃炒麵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說貝內迪克特 你幹嘛插話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幹嘛這麼兇啊 太不給面子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不如 大家一起逛節日市場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 謝謝妳的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我等下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還要去排練下個月上映的戲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是妳寫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 不過是在公民館上的一個小劇場而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有空的話來看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就先這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要時刻都記著 願望就會實現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也有時刻記著 但不會實現的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}代筆的工作已經堆積如山了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少今天給自己放個假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難得有節日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這會影響到我的工作計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我還是回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}丟下我快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.85,0:22:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絕對…絕對不會讓少校死的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.26,0:22:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}停下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快給我停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.42,0:22:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.59,0:22:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尋找妳自己的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.53,0:22:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我從心底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.81,0:22:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛著妳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.18,0:23:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「親愛的吉爾貝特少校
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天又不禁想起了少校您
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無論看到什麼 在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.47,0:23:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我總會不自覺地聯想起您
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.53,0:23:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使那些時光再怎麼消磨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.71,0:23:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}與您一起的回憶總能清晰地回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您把我放在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.74,0:24:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}教會一無所知的我該去如何生存
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.36,0:24:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還第一次把
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.65,0:24:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.51,0:24:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這三個字告訴給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.80,0:24:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一想到這 我又不禁寫起信來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.59,0:24:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希望有一天 您能收到這封信
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.85,0:24:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也希望我的願望會有實現的一日」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.37,0:25:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您好 這是3科西嘉的找零
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.24,0:25:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝您的光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.96,0:25:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}重量是1.2里布盧 費用是11科西嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.41,0:25:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您好 CH郵局
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.77,0:25:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若客有所求 則使命必達
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.02,0:25:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是自動手記人偶服務的愛麗絲·坎納利
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.02,0:25:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的 她在
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.24,0:25:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉久等了 很不湊巧您指定的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.99,0:25:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}預約已經排滿3個月了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.37,0:25:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您看我能為您服務嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.60,0:25:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.09,0:25:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.66,0:26:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼幫您安排3個月後的預約
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.23,0:26:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.76,0:26:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.04,0:26:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.58,0:26:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳這態度對客人太沒禮貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.63,0:26:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他隔著電話又看不到我啥態度
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.53,0:26:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳什麼表情都體現在聲音上了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.71,0:26:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.29,0:26:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再說 妳的預約也不是很滿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.75,0:26:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有妳那麼滿
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.29,0:26:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣下去 我永遠是這裡的老三啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.30,0:26:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.80,0:26:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}社長 你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.84,0:26:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這週也忙壞了吧 大傢伙明天好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.92,0:26:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我這週末可是要出差
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.88,0:26:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不是要我給加爾達尼克的貿易條約修改會議當書記嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.73,0:27:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確實是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.08,0:27:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要出席市長夫人的派對
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.57,0:27:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給郵局開發一下新客戶
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.98,0:27:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳們都很熱愛工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.39,0:27:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最近我開始打網球
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.65,0:27:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還想著有誰能陪我練一下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.22,0:27:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}社長你就沒有危機感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.32,0:27:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還不趁現在好好拚搏一番
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.40,0:27:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就因為那個討厭的機器
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.15,0:27:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}書信這東西遲早會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.16,0:27:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}信號塔也快建好了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.91,0:27:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以後電話肯定會普及得更廣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.15,0:27:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.44,0:28:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很多東西都在改變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.51,0:28:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個郵局也開始有了些變化
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.70,0:28:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或許有一天這份工作會變得古老落後
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.12,0:28:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人偶也是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.72,0:28:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後被淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.48,0:28:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最後消失不見
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.82,0:28:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.48,0:28:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才要趁現在多賺錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.39,0:28:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以說 薇爾莉特也要去派對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.19,0:28:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.99,0:28:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才不要把競爭對手帶去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.86,0:28:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的 那我就不去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.40,0:28:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛好我也需要外出一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.14,0:28:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.74,0:28:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼啊 能不能再慢點打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.22,0:28:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是跟女孩打 那還算有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.00,0:28:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但誰讓你是社長
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.65,0:29:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她們都很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.09,0:29:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特也沒空跟我打
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.79,0:29:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這不挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.20,0:29:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她有事出去還挺少見的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.68,0:29:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過她要是來了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.11,0:29:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或許更容易勾到其他女生的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.21,0:29:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}派件的時候經常被問到
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.45,0:29:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是CH郵局的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.68,0:29:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快把你們家叫薇爾莉特的人偶介紹給我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.24,0:29:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不許你把薇爾莉特用在不純的動機上
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.89,0:29:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.86,0:29:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她這是上哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.92,0:29:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你太過保護她了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.23,0:30:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上校
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.06,0:30:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來是妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.82,0:30:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每個月的忌日都給我媽獻花
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.50,0:30:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本來應該是明天來的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.08,0:30:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但考慮到當天會有親戚在場
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.60,0:30:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我為難到您了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.87,0:30:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.93,0:30:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但也沒必要特地跑來這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.68,0:30:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天可是休息日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.55,0:30:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為是休息日才能來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.34,0:30:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳是代替他來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.42,0:30:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這並非是代替少校的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.38,0:30:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我按照自己的意願要來的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.38,0:31:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戰爭結束後已經過去多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.64,0:31:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳應該清楚吧 他已經
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.97,0:31:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忘掉吉爾伯特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.00,0:31:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忘掉他很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.97,0:31:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.48,0:31:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就沒辦法忘掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.97,0:31:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.81,0:32:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.81,0:32:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs38}Violet
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.43,0:32:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對 那不是紫羅蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.43,0:32:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs38\pos(1090,740)}Violet
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.34,0:32:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而是叫三色堇
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.71,0:32:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎 你知道的真多
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.64,0:32:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算沒辦法再見面
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.50,0:32:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忘掉他很困難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.05,0:33:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}髮帶
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.53,0:33:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您好 CH郵局…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.22,0:33:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 請問有人偶在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.81,0:33:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.38,0:33:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.72,0:33:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我有東西想委託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.37,0:33:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能來我這邊一趟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.42,0:33:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天我們公司休息
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.98,0:33:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.29,0:33:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.23,0:33:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.62,0:33:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽您聲音 應該年紀很小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.08,0:33:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寫封信還跟年紀有關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.35,0:33:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人偶不是有所需就使命必達嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.22,0:33:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是騙人的？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.10,0:33:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 那不是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.24,0:33:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那快來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.42,0:34:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.80,0:34:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是CH郵局的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.00,0:34:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.37,0:34:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.01,0:34:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.54,0:34:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若客有所求 則使命必達
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.17,0:34:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是自動手記人偶服務的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.63,0:34:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特·伊芙嘉登
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.80,0:34:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.93,0:34:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為是客人您要求的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.08,0:35:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}年紀小不成問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.12,0:35:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會盡全力的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.11,0:35:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.57,0:35:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.73,0:35:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我開門了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.98,0:35:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先等等
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.23,0:35:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}藏起來 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.68,0:35:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.74,0:35:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.54,0:35:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤里斯 有人來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.86,0:35:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.98,0:35:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.65,0:35:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我聽見有說話的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.04,0:35:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.89,0:35:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別每天都問一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.36,0:35:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.92,0:35:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事的話還會躺在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.98,0:35:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.52,0:35:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.36,0:35:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我給你念繪本
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.01,0:36:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰要聽繪本啊 無聊死了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.45,0:36:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你哥哥身體不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.36,0:36:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何止不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.27,0:36:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手術做了3次 醫院躺了1年
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.67,0:36:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤里斯 說起來路卡他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.30,0:36:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想來探望探望你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.07,0:36:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}似乎是挺想你的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.81,0:36:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用來
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.55,0:36:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼 你們關係不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.07,0:36:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都說不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.29,0:36:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.71,0:36:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都破了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.24,0:36:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別亂摸 傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.69,0:36:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.47,0:36:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隔壁房間來看我時落下的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.88,0:36:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只是代為保管而已
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.35,0:36:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.54,0:36:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我睏了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.90,0:37:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起 媽媽我們去散會兒步
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.82,0:37:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是 睡一會兒也好
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.17,0:37:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們等下再來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.17,0:37:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.30,0:37:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.37,0:37:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼我必須藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.27,0:37:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以把原因告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.67,0:37:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.52,0:37:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫尤里斯就行
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.60,0:37:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼 尤里斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.05,0:37:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想讓爸媽還有弟弟知道
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.71,0:37:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是指寫信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.97,0:37:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我想給他們3人寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.29,0:38:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想等我死了以後才讓他們看到信
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.96,0:38:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以寫好後幫忙保管一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.33,0:38:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不需要馬上寄出去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.50,0:38:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.23,0:38:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.08,0:38:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這能辦到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.84,0:38:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.29,0:38:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前也有承接過同樣的委託
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.10,0:38:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有一個比您年紀稍小的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.08,0:38:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她媽媽打算給她寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.28,0:38:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使她媽媽不在這個世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.13,0:38:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她50年內 每年生日都會收到她媽媽的信
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.66,0:38:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}50年內…有50封？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.04,0:38:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.54,0:38:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在每年生日 她應該都會收到媽媽的信
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.63,0:39:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思啊 我寫不了那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.85,0:39:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}錢都在那個罐子裡 能寫多少寫多少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.81,0:39:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這些錢能寫多少
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.61,0:39:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寫3封的話
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.64,0:39:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每封大概20字左右
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.78,0:39:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}20字？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.09,0:39:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給媽媽 請保重 尤里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.09,0:39:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太短
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.49,0:39:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣我也能寫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.51,0:39:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是 我想爸媽和弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.04,0:39:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讀了後能夠打起精神重新生活
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.08,0:39:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想寫這樣的信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.70,0:39:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤里斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.30,0:39:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才的是一般的費用
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.45,0:39:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我們公司有兒童優惠
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.02,0:39:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以 罐子裡的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.72,0:40:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以寫出讓您滿意的信件
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.16,0:40:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.48,0:40:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.86,0:40:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別糊弄我了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.92,0:40:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}並沒有糊弄您
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.94,0:40:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了順利完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.52,0:40:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公司定下了特殊情況時適用的特別規定
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.52,0:40:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這份緊急措施
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.73,0:40:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒聽懂
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.43,0:40:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之就是有戲唄
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.36,0:40:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是行的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.48,0:40:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.20,0:40:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳的手
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.13,0:40:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戰爭中失去的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.54,0:41:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}數年前 我也曾住進醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.33,0:41:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳這手能寫信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.81,0:41:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了熟練使用這副義手
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.30,0:41:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}花費了我不少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.90,0:41:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在已經不成問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.43,0:41:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我還能做這樣的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.61,0:41:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳還挺有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.11,0:41:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳和總是重複「感覺怎麼樣」
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.99,0:41:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「沒事吧」「好好休息吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.01,0:41:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這三句臺詞的爸媽還有護士稍微不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.19,0:41:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}稍微不同是指
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.28,0:41:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}擔心和同情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.25,0:41:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}過度保護？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.44,0:41:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之 我已經受夠那些了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.16,0:41:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.64,0:41:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我寫信時儘可能地把這3點排除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.56,0:41:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳真的太有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.73,0:41:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 那就
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.66,0:42:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幫我寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.77,0:42:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.79,0:42:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.90,0:42:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 爸爸去打仗了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.31,0:42:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去了一個叫萊頓夏福特利的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.83,0:42:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他說過馬上就回來 但一直沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.48,0:42:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我想告訴爸爸 我和弟弟還有媽媽都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.11,0:42:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能幫我寫信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.76,0:42:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫上薇爾莉特吃頓飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.80,0:42:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就去那個地方吧 那個餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.56,0:42:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她來到這裡第一次去的那個餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.94,0:42:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.30,0:42:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}迪特弗利特上校
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.87,0:43:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}霍金斯中校
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.77,0:43:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對 你現在是社長
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.27,0:43:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我總是忘記戰爭已經過去很多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.81,0:43:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有何貴幹
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.70,0:43:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.05,0:43:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.79,0:43:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上校
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.72,0:43:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.68,0:43:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我冒犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.52,0:43:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.29,0:43:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.28,0:43:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.80,0:43:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您專門給我送來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.40,0:44:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我發現妳把這個落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.26,0:44:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特外出的地方 該不會是
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.44,0:44:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}墓園
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.09,0:44:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校媽媽墓地所在的墓園
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.00,0:44:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上校 謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.55,0:44:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.92,0:44:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把行李放下 一起吃個飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.86,0:44:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.88,0:44:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特妳也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.38,0:44:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.37,0:44:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等下
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.74,0:44:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我家有艘船準備要處分掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.08,0:44:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}船嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.59,0:44:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是他小時候經常坐的船
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.96,0:45:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}裡面有他經常看的書和玩的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.62,0:45:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是妳有想要的話
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.33,0:45:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.53,0:45:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但都是些破爛
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.22,0:45:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.46,0:45:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您船停在哪 我直接過去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.01,0:45:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來妳每個月都去掃墓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.74,0:45:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這應該報告給您嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.68,0:45:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 不用
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.25,0:45:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用報告
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.36,0:45:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這叫個人隱私好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.58,0:45:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼…船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.14,0:45:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去的時候跟您報告
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.02,0:45:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都說不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.69,0:45:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.36,0:45:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.07,0:45:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.73,0:45:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對我的擔心 同情和過度保護
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.74,0:45:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使您儘可能全部去掉 我也能行
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.29,0:46:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家說能行
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.51,0:46:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就你多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.83,0:46:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}閉嘴快吃吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.73,0:46:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特說的沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.11,0:46:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不應該總是這麼擔心她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.90,0:46:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這誰不擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.27,0:46:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而是迪特弗利特那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.59,0:46:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}居然對薇爾莉特趁虛而入
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.77,0:46:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對薇爾莉特來說興許是個不錯的傾訴對象
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.78,0:46:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟能互相傾訴少校的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.57,0:46:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那人看上薇爾莉特是孤兒這點
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.97,0:46:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收留之後就把她當成戰爭的道具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.20,0:46:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以你才不讓他接近薇爾莉特？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.25,0:46:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使現在他沒有這麼幹也？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.01,0:46:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道你想讓那兩人相互療癒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.28,0:46:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是壞事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.11,0:47:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在薇爾莉特還想著少校
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.46,0:47:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣下去 我擔心她遲早會崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.01,0:47:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但上校可以給她我們給不了的安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.22,0:47:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是將來我有了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.04,0:47:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是想要個兒子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.45,0:47:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是女兒 我的神經可頂不住
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.06,0:47:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是他非常喜歡的一本書
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.57,0:47:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也經常和爸爸一起玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.51,0:47:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這也是少校的？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.30,0:48:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 這是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.70,0:48:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.91,0:48:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用這麼拘謹
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.27,0:48:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.59,0:48:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上校和少校小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.64,0:48:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}經常坐這艘船出海吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.24,0:48:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 被爸爸帶出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.14,0:48:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我爸一心只想著陸軍
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.99,0:48:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道為什麼總喜歡出海
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.42,0:48:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我繼承下的也僅有這些
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.94,0:49:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是我們家的花
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.33,0:49:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼叫我們家的花
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.61,0:49:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你剛才說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.32,0:49:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想讓我們看的是那些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.59,0:49:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是想讓我倆也成為像你一樣的軍人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.37,0:49:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.70,0:49:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們的選擇只有那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.82,0:49:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是想讓我們知道這點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.46,0:49:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.10,0:49:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你和你爸爸 還有我們布甘比利亞家一族
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.20,0:49:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}除了參軍就無路可走了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.25,0:49:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.11,0:49:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要打哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.98,0:50:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我當
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.90,0:50:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會成為像你一樣的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.58,0:50:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概我當時有多抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.89,0:50:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吉爾無奈服從我爸時就有多認真吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.34,0:50:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我的錯 弟弟的人生被套上枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.42,0:50:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而我對他的態度卻只有作嘔二字可以形容
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.57,0:50:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒有兄弟姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.99,0:50:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不太明白您說的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.00,0:50:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為都是至親
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.67,0:50:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難免會產生複雜的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.18,0:50:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這點我能稍微理解
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.35,0:50:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳能理解人的心情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.10,0:50:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是 我沒有諷刺的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.39,0:50:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.57,0:51:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能收下這本書和這個遊戲板嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.56,0:51:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.14,0:51:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.91,0:51:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.24,0:51:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.34,0:51:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}失去的東西太沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.22,0:51:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳也是 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.60,0:51:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.44,0:51:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說了永遠見不了和忘掉他之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.15,0:51:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實我自己也忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.09,0:52:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終究其因 那是我弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.56,0:52:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.56,0:52:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下次再見 我還有事情要向妳道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.82,0:52:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有事情想和妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.85,0:52:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.48,0:52:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下來是弟弟的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.91,0:52:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是 該寫什麼給弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.89,0:52:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}紫苑也才5歲
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.41,0:52:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼 把弟弟剛出生時的感受寫進信裡如何
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.45,0:52:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他出生時我可高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.20,0:52:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像剛出爐的麵包一樣 暖烘烘的軟綿綿的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.53,0:52:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.92,0:52:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}漸漸父母的關愛都被奪走的感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.80,0:53:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.37,0:53:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弟弟被稱讚反而覺得無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.26,0:53:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說對了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.10,0:53:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但過後弟弟追過來時 卻覺得很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.34,0:53:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.74,0:53:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼這麼懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.36,0:53:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是聽回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.27,0:53:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那剛才的再加上一段
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.40,0:53:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「把我的生命也活出來
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.19,0:53:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有 你要替我 跟爸爸媽媽搞好關係」
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.15,0:53:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「你要替我
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.60,0:53:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好跟爸爸媽媽撒嬌」
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.28,0:53:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我看出來
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.39,0:53:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你其實是很想撒嬌的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.80,0:54:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一時嘴快才把違心的話傾瀉在他們身上
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.03,0:54:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳真是什麼都懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.20,0:54:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我寫過很多信件
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.17,0:54:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}言語也好 態度也好 感情也好
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.97,0:54:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都有內外兩面
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.10,0:54:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}眼睛看到的不代表全部
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.29,0:54:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是我漸漸悟到的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.60,0:54:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但心裡真正想的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.41,0:54:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不說出來 很多時候是不會懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.50,0:54:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼 這樣您看可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.44,0:54:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.97,0:55:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼這3封信件 就由我們代為保管
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.41,0:55:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.28,0:55:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我去了天國那天再派給大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.13,0:55:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會讓醫院通知你們郵局的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.25,0:55:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.39,0:55:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說 妳能拉鈎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.93,0:55:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拉鈎？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.23,0:55:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對 小拇指和小拇指
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.59,0:55:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像這樣勾起來
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.48,0:55:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後互相發誓一定要遵守約定
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.62,0:55:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.13,0:55:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷的手指啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.87,0:56:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戴著手套也感覺得到
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.14,0:56:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冬天來臨前 我肯定也會變得冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.19,0:56:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.03,0:56:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您留下的信件
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.46,0:56:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也一定能溫暖父母和弟弟的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.98,0:56:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定會把信件送到的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.17,0:56:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼 我的任務就此結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.75,0:56:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.77,0:57:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我還有一封信想寫
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.44,0:57:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是路卡先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.73,0:57:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在床下時聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.29,0:57:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.60,0:57:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想說的話 趁著能說的時候先說了會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.12,0:57:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.79,0:57:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.69,0:57:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想問的沒問全 想說的沒說完
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.16,0:57:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.12,0:57:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}教會我如何去愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.77,0:57:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.78,0:57:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.38,0:57:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}相信他一定活在某個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.77,0:57:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳想對他說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.18,0:58:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想說 我稍微懂得了愛
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.72,0:58:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是懂了而已？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.33,0:58:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}路卡說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.08,0:58:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他想來看望我
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.01,0:58:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我卻讓他別來
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.48,0:58:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和他從小關係就很好
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.66,0:58:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}經常一起到處跑來跑去
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.85,0:58:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我的手和腳
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.65,0:58:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}卻變得好細
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.90,0:58:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想讓他看到我這副樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.59,0:58:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可以把你這感情寫在信件上
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.11,0:58:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}費用是
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.72,0:59:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤里斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.53,0:59:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去叫護士
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.62,0:59:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給路卡先生的信件就等到下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.17,0:59:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.14,0:59:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.86,1:00:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這些全都不知道收件人啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.48,1:00:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是羅蘭爺留下的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.84,1:00:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我打算有發件人的就返回去
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.27,1:00:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以呢 你讓我這社長幫忙？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.39,1:00:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在的年輕人都不喜歡加班
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.60,1:00:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看我這麼敬業的份上
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.31,1:00:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好歹把我升上副社長
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.43,1:00:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你給我去上個簿記學校
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.69,1:00:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}賬本都看不明白怎麼當副社長
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.88,1:00:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我看到通往成功的路了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.46,1:00:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就去上上看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.75,1:00:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.30,1:01:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這邊基本都放著近期的郵件
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.49,1:01:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這字跡
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.56,1:01:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.35,1:01:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.71,1:01:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寄件人的地址在依卡特島
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.37,1:01:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是之前被加達里克佔領的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.36,1:01:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像戰爭後獨立出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.45,1:01:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來找我有何貴幹 社長大人
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.73,1:01:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前些天…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.98,1:01:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想說你家人偶的事？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.94,1:01:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.02,1:01:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.52,1:01:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.43,1:01:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到我船上拿完東西後
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.28,1:01:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就說社長擔心她 然後就走了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.34,1:01:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還說去的時候會給我報告啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.66,1:01:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不是她的監護人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.71,1:02:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你沒權利束縛她
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.12,1:02:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.64,1:02:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}輪不到你這傢伙說
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.70,1:02:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.85,1:02:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我失言了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.46,1:02:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的錯 找不到別的說法了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.00,1:02:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.14,1:02:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是為了薇爾莉特的事情來的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.73,1:02:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.57,1:02:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能幫我查查嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.01,1:02:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}社長
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.98,1:03:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼晚了抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.44,1:03:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有話想跟妳說
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.22,1:03:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.63,1:03:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還沒有十成的把握
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.62,1:03:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能是搞錯了也說不定
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.99,1:03:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是少校…嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.19,1:03:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.67,1:03:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.48,1:03:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道吉爾伯特少校的什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.30,1:04:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以要現在去嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.28,1:04:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對 有可能是搞錯
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.93,1:04:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但還是去看看
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.65,1:04:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.03,1:04:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}工作方面就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.32,1:04:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特 還好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.89,1:04:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.68,1:04:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可以見少校嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.10,1:04:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒有什麼奇怪的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.40,1:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經過去好長時間了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.38,1:05:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校還認得我嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.44,1:05:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說…薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.91,1:05:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見面後應該先說什麼才好呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.63,1:05:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是該匯報現狀嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.94,1:05:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是說此刻的心情？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.53,1:05:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這些我都能順利表達出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.31,1:05:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會不會覺得我噁心
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.20,1:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.63,1:05:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}目的地還很遠
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.76,1:05:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}路上不如寫封信吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.35,1:05:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們回來了 黛西
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.41,1:05:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉我們回來晚了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.61,1:05:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黛西？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.74,1:06:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要去萊頓一段時間
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.44,1:06:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她工作的郵局
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.50,1:06:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和其他公司一起成為了國企
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.93,1:06:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原本的建築則成為了博物館
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.98,1:07:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}離開這裡後 她到底去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.59,1:07:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}慢慢參觀吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.36,1:07:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.41,1:07:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.78,1:07:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什麼想問的請儘管開口
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.90,1:07:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實我以前在這裡幹過前臺
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.69,1:07:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.77,1:07:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.94,1:08:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請問 這枚郵票
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.56,1:08:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.32,1:08:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只在依卡特島發行的郵票
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.14,1:08:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}依卡特島？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.91,1:08:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請問
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.06,1:08:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您剛才說您在這工作過是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.32,1:08:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.83,1:08:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}慷慨的大海啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.69,1:08:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}連接整個世界的大海啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.69,1:08:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海鷗在飛舞 在您的上空中
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.82,1:08:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}魚兒在暢遊 在您的身體中
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.08,1:08:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貝殼在隱藏 在您的最底裡
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.03,1:09:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您給予光明
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.94,1:09:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您孕育生命
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.43,1:09:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您傾注愛意
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.32,1:09:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我與您相依相偎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.36,1:09:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.32,1:09:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您包容下過去和未來
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.05,1:09:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我將把自己託付於您的定奪
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.38,1:10:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本來這裡是感謝大海的儀式地
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.14,1:10:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在卻變成了未歸之人的弔唁地
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.96,1:10:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰都沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.51,1:10:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}島上只剩下老人和女人
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.12,1:10:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有孩子罷了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.80,1:10:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}葬身的不是大海 而是戰場
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.10,1:10:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣該怎麼給祖先做交代啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.59,1:10:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸他們是被萊頓的士兵殺死的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.33,1:10:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.93,1:10:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}萊頓的人全死掉才好
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.63,1:10:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才朗讀的是
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.72,1:10:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今年萊頓的感謝日中獻給大海的讚歌
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.29,1:10:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽說是很有名的人偶寫的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.07,1:10:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是叫薇爾莉特·伊芙嘉登
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.66,1:11:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大伙兒們
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.49,1:11:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來 吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.22,1:11:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走吧 吃飯去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.93,1:11:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.52,1:11:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最喜歡老師了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.07,1:11:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快 我們去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.85,1:11:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來啊來啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.95,1:11:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「少校 真的好長時間沒見了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.04,1:11:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有見到您的這段期間
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.34,1:11:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我每天每天都在想著您
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.81,1:12:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以 我不斷地祈禱
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.86,1:12:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不斷地許願
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.12,1:12:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希望有一天我們能再見」
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.65,1:13:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.94,1:13:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳能在這等我一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.09,1:13:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.03,1:13:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是吉爾伯特真的在這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.62,1:13:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們也不知道他現在是什麼狀況
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.98,1:13:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以…
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.81,1:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.50,1:13:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳可能不介意
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.22,1:13:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但他不好說
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.55,1:13:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他似乎沒有在這裡用真名
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.65,1:13:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個島很小
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.89,1:13:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}應該不想被人說閒話吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.59,1:14:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳在這裡等一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.94,1:14:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我等
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.40,1:14:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是能見到少校的話
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.01,1:14:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多久我都等
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.90,1:14:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是第一次來
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.13,1:14:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不妳去周圍逛逛
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.20,1:14:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.08,1:15:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不認識那大叔啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.54,1:15:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.33,1:15:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.95,1:15:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.34,1:15:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不…不是
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.96,1:15:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.13,1:15:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很可疑
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.78,1:15:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是 我是郵局來的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.53,1:16:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就是來送信的囉
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.91,1:16:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.75,1:16:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對了 給你個好東西
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.88,1:16:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嚇死他了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.89,1:16:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-走吧 -好
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.84,1:16:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兒子我的神經也受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.70,1:16:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰的姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.90,1:16:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.01,1:16:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}郵局來的？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.73,1:16:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.72,1:16:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就知道
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.74,1:16:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給你個好東西
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.68,1:16:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.99,1:16:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昆蟲
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.08,1:16:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是螳螂嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.64,1:16:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳不怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.62,1:16:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前腳少了一根
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.30,1:16:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 和格爾伯特老師一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.12,1:17:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那位老師
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.12,1:17:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}右眼也…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.57,1:17:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這也知道啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.03,1:17:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那位老師是大家的老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.25,1:17:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.15,1:17:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老師他
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.90,1:17:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一切都好嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.09,1:17:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 雖然沒有右手
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.41,1:17:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但單靠左手就能做引體向上
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.91,1:17:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跑步也很快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.57,1:17:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 超級快的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.66,1:17:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.97,1:17:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.22,1:17:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以 可以再給我講講你們的老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.50,1:17:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.08,1:17:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}首先啊 老師他非常溫柔
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.51,1:17:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有不懂的地方會教到懂為止
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.26,1:18:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.70,1:18:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}進來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.54,1:19:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是有哪裡不懂的話
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.80,1:19:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我實在想不到
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.37,1:19:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你竟然活著
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.70,1:19:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吉爾伯特
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.07,1:19:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在這裡我自稱格爾伯特
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.12,1:19:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.22,1:19:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉來得這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.33,1:19:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼知道是這
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.86,1:19:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你幫孩子代過筆吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.92,1:19:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收件人不明的信件會回到郵局
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.46,1:19:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}返還給發件人前會再確認一次
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.27,1:20:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恰巧看到那封信
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.72,1:20:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反倒是你 為什麼在這
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.77,1:20:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那場決戰後
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.03,1:20:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我醒過來就在醫院的床上了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.25,1:20:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為沒有狗牌
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.59,1:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以被送到修道會的醫院了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.42,1:20:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當我給醫院幫忙了一段時間後
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.14,1:20:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒有回到祖國 而是輾轉南北
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.50,1:20:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1年前 我來到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.24,1:21:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在孩子們的請求下不斷地寫著信
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.08,1:21:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最後便有了這學校
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.55,1:21:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本來我應該給軍隊報告
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.28,1:21:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別管這個了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.20,1:21:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道薇爾莉特還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.02,1:21:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.75,1:21:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.96,1:21:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不去看她一眼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.86,1:21:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特她…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.65,1:21:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她一直都在等著你…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.97,1:21:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我令她陷入不幸的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.95,1:21:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我離開她是最好的選擇
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.67,1:21:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她這次也來了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.86,1:21:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在就在外面等著
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.19,1:21:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道她有多想見到你嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.96,1:22:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見不了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.64,1:22:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吉爾伯特
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.24,1:22:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}永遠都見不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.35,1:22:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.22,1:22:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經死了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.81,1:22:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吉爾伯特·布甘比利亞已經死了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.24,1:22:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.57,1:22:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}過了這麼多年 大家都應該接受我的死了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.50,1:22:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以你讓我過上別的人生吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.25,1:22:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吉爾伯特…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.73,1:22:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在 是葡萄的收獲季節
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.01,1:22:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等下我要去幫忙
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.98,1:22:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這座島嶼的男人全都打仗去了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.68,1:22:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但一個都沒回來
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.17,1:22:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}霍金斯 求你了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.97,1:23:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}改天 我再來
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.09,1:23:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳…有沒有在憎恨我？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.83,1:23:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不明白問題的含義
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.41,1:23:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是不是做錯了什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.74,1:23:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是做錯了我可以改
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.92,1:23:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請您告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.45,1:23:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.13,1:23:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}錯的是
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.89,1:23:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一邊說著妳不是道具
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.37,1:23:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一邊使用著妳的我
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.13,1:24:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}使用我沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.65,1:24:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我是少校的武器
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.59,1:24:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戰況似乎對我軍不利
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.32,1:24:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下一步該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.66,1:24:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校 請給我命令
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.83,1:24:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}社長
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.68,1:24:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是少校
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.20,1:24:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然是少校沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.65,1:24:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我從小孩口中打聽到了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.86,1:24:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您已經見到少校了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.06,1:24:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.21,1:25:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}除了手臂和眼睛受傷以外
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.22,1:25:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有另外的受傷了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.18,1:25:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.22,1:25:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.73,1:25:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能去見他了對吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.57,1:25:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.60,1:25:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他說見不了妳
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.47,1:25:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他現在還在執行任務嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.51,1:25:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣的話我等他任務結束
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.31,1:25:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.75,1:25:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就等到晚上
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.77,1:25:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.25,1:25:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那…那就等到明天
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.69,1:25:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.05,1:25:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天我再去找他談談看
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.88,1:25:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他必須要見妳
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.53,1:25:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那按照我的推測
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.10,1:26:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校不是不能見我
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.03,1:26:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而是不想見我 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.22,1:26:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.83,1:26:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說不清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.78,1:26:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但他說這對雙方都好
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.49,1:26:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一點不好
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.98,1:26:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我 我…
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.96,1:26:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.38,1:26:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.39,1:26:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這機器要是做好了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.13,1:26:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就能很方便往上面運葡萄了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.74,1:26:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.91,1:27:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看來是一場大雨
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.76,1:27:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.34,1:27:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.38,1:27:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找到他了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.45,1:28:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.58,1:28:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.90,1:28:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.38,1:28:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.02,1:28:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.52,1:28:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉打擾到您家了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.34,1:28:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校 您要是活著
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.02,1:28:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼不聯繫我呢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.57,1:28:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼不來見我呢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.10,1:28:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我非常想見您
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.32,1:29:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還想繼續聊最後沒聊完的話題
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.67,1:29:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有 我也稍微懂得了什麼是愛
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.85,1:29:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回去
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.05,1:29:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給我回去
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.28,1:29:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我等
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.98,1:29:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等到您願意見我為止
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.88,1:29:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就在這等
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.45,1:29:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在的妳不需要我
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.33,1:29:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且一看到妳 我就會回想起來
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.72,1:29:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是怎麼把年幼的妳送上戰場的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.41,1:30:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳聽了我的命令
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.94,1:30:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}失去了雙手
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.55,1:30:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校您是在後悔是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.29,1:30:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的存在…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.81,1:30:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我讓少校
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.59,1:30:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感到痛苦了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.18,1:30:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在的我能理解少校您的心情
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.40,1:30:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然可能不是全部
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.42,1:30:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但至少有一點點
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.22,1:31:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這個大混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.64,1:32:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這些儘管用吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.65,1:32:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.19,1:32:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也只有妳這裡能收留我們了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.45,1:32:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟這小島連住宿都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.39,1:33:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.95,1:33:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽說這個燈塔還同時是郵局
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.65,1:33:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.66,1:33:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又到這種花綻放的季節了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.56,1:33:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}王子的雙眼是碧藍的藍寶石
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.16,1:33:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}腰上別著的劍綻放著紅寶石的赤色光芒
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.75,1:33:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在已經讀得很流暢了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.63,1:33:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.88,1:33:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別離開我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.19,1:33:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要一直待在我身邊 薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.39,1:34:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.68,1:34:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們是萊頓郵局的？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.46,1:34:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 對
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.30,1:34:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特·伊芙嘉登是
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.79,1:34:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才的女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.17,1:34:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}郵局說醫院來了聯絡
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.05,1:34:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說一個叫尤里斯的男孩病危了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.84,1:34:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤里斯？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.85,1:34:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.73,1:34:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是我的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.12,1:34:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}客人
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.86,1:34:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我去了天國那天再派給大家吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.00,1:35:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.20,1:35:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們回去
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.95,1:35:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們回去萊頓
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.16,1:35:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.04,1:35:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼回去 現在可是暴風雨啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.68,1:35:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少要等到天亮 不然是沒船的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.35,1:35:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳不是要見吉爾伯特嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.85,1:35:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想見
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.76,1:35:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想見啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.70,1:35:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.49,1:36:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們拉過勾了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.29,1:36:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和尤里斯先生已經約好了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.74,1:36:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且 我還有一封信沒寫
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.33,1:36:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是回去再快也要花3天
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.50,1:36:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再快點
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.21,1:36:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.73,1:36:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才貝內迪克特拿著保管的信件
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.27,1:36:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和愛麗絲一起往醫院趕了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.30,1:37:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.26,1:37:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.18,1:37:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤里斯
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.86,1:37:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人偶已經來了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.46,1:37:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不是有信要寫嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.34,1:37:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.07,1:37:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是代替她的愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.74,1:37:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特現在在遠方
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.16,1:37:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她終於見到了最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.34,1:38:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}教會她如何去愛的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.80,1:38:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.16,1:38:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.95,1:38:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.57,1:38:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我都聽她說了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.37,1:38:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要給路卡寫信對吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.15,1:38:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.41,1:38:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要寫什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.66,1:38:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤里斯
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.01,1:38:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤里斯
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.33,1:39:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤里斯
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.57,1:39:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經不要緊了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.10,1:39:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.26,1:40:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麻煩幫忙連線 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.54,1:40:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤里斯 是路卡
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.55,1:40:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這 這個
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.25,1:40:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該怎麼弄
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.27,1:40:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該說喂
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.60,1:40:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤里斯？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.32,1:40:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.72,1:40:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.15,1:40:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}路卡？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.15,1:40:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說別來看我
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.03,1:40:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不想見你什麼的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.90,1:40:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.24,1:40:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.19,1:41:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.89,1:41:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.60,1:41:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽到你說不想見我 雖然很傷心
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.39,1:41:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我相信一定是你覺得這樣對大家都好
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.17,1:41:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我忍耐了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.39,1:41:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是最後還是忍不了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.50,1:41:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去了好幾趟醫院
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.82,1:41:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後從窗戶稍微看到了你的臉
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.66,1:41:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 我說得太過份了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.88,1:41:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.88,1:41:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一點都不生氣
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.12,1:41:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤里斯
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.41,1:41:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們一直都是好朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.93,1:41:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以後也要是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.26,1:42:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.73,1:42:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.76,1:42:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.14,1:42:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個討人厭的機器也挺好用嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.93,1:42:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤里斯
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.05,1:42:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤里斯
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.99,1:42:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤里斯！
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.31,1:43:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}信沒有寫成
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.24,1:43:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是最後
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.96,1:43:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用電話和路卡說上了話
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.10,1:43:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經把想說的都說出去了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.08,1:43:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他的抱歉和謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.73,1:43:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後妳寫的信件
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.99,1:43:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也都已經交給他父母和弟弟了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.07,1:44:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「媽媽做的烙餅很好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.56,1:44:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是多吃一點青菜
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.75,1:44:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽會不會高興
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.43,1:44:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸 釣魚和露營都很好玩
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.31,1:44:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能當爸爸和媽媽的孩子實在太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.48,1:44:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我愛你們 尤里斯」
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.53,1:45:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有一封信是給弟弟的
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.47,1:45:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.69,1:45:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「紫苑
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.73,1:45:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉老是罵你 捉弄你
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.99,1:45:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是你出生的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.56,1:45:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我真的非常高興
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.07,1:45:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你把我當哥哥看
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.37,1:45:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把我的生命也活出來
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.87,1:45:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有 你要替我保護好爸爸媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.82,1:45:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還要搞好關係
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.81,1:45:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好跟爸爸媽媽撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.44,1:45:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給我最愛的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.14,1:46:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的哥哥」
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.27,1:46:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.83,1:46:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好高興
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.81,1:46:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸和媽媽也很高興吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.10,1:46:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你 尤里斯
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.79,1:46:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤里斯他聽說妳見到了最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.30,1:46:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}高興得不得了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.18,1:46:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等天亮了 再去找他一次吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.07,1:47:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是不出來 就把門踢破
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.49,1:47:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後把那傢伙揍一頓
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.76,1:47:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.65,1:47:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要揍少校的話 就由我來
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.02,1:47:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇…
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.46,1:47:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.62,1:47:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天就坐船回去
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.01,1:47:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回郵局去
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.86,1:47:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回去後就開始寫信
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.88,1:47:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}工作已經堆積了很多
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.39,1:47:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.41,1:47:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校他活得很好
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.36,1:47:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我還以為這輩子已經再也見不到他了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.47,1:47:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還聽到了他的聲音
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.99,1:47:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…已經
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.23,1:48:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}十分滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.07,1:49:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎樣 給我示範一次
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.23,1:49:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來了 上來了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.99,1:49:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.04,1:49:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是啊 這樣一來就輕鬆多了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.68,1:49:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是郵局的大叔和姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.40,1:49:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大叔…
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.07,1:49:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快看 那個機器是老師做的
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.17,1:50:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-好厲害 -太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.87,1:50:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-快看 好多啊 -還能再裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.56,1:50:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太強了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.01,1:50:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太厲害了 我也想坐進去
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.15,1:50:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對吧 很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.66,1:50:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.71,1:50:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個能幫我交給老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.99,1:50:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道啦 一定幫妳交給他
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.87,1:50:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜拜啦
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.78,1:51:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不應該一個人扛下來
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.05,1:51:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這座小島全部青年都消失了也好
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.81,1:51:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那場大戰中眾多人犧牲了也罷
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.92,1:51:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或許是我們這一輩犯下的錯
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.19,1:51:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打仗便會富裕
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.77,1:51:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.78,1:51:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都覺得萊頓夏福特利的人都該死
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.81,1:51:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.14,1:51:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到最後所有人都受傷了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.96,1:51:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是所有人
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.06,1:52:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是有家可歸的話我勸你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.09,1:52:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有 我就待在這
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.60,1:52:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這輩子都待在這
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.24,1:52:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那真是幫大忙了
Comment: 0,1:52:37.69,1:52:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.89,1:52:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在這個小島
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.58,1:52:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你終於能過上自己的人生了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.18,1:52:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確實是個好地方
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.72,1:53:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.61,1:53:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明過得逍遙自在
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.17,1:53:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}連媽媽的葬禮都沒出席
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.71,1:53:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我不一樣 你不是被疼愛著的一方嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.95,1:53:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.48,1:53:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}罷 薇爾莉特已經替你拜訪媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.47,1:53:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在她每個月都會去掃墓
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.48,1:53:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直想著 要是還能見到
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.93,1:53:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要好好向你道歉來著
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.00,1:53:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.16,1:53:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在我想把你裝進麻袋
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.91,1:53:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後丟在薇爾莉特的面前
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.40,1:53:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那時候
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.09,1:53:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不應該收留下她的
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.18,1:54:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你到底想怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.43,1:54:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那時候她還很小
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.78,1:54:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我應該讓她度過更快樂的時間
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.11,1:54:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像可愛的東西
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.61,1:54:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}應該得到疼愛
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.60,1:54:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}美麗的東西
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.82,1:54:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}應該歡欣雀躍一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.87,1:54:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我本想讓她擁有這樣的童年
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.11,1:54:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.67,1:55:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的信 看看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.09,1:55:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「親愛的吉爾伯特少校
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.56,1:55:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請原諒我的突然造訪
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.72,1:55:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是我給您寫的最後一封信了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.22,1:55:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我現在可以活著
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.28,1:55:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能夠去思念某一個人
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.51,1:55:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都要歸功於少校您
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.01,1:56:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝您接納我
Dialogue: 0,1:56:08.25,1:56:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給我讀書
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.72,1:56:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}教會我讀書識字
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.55,1:56:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感謝您
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.63,1:56:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為我購買胸針
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.69,1:56:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感謝您
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.93,1:56:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直…
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.01,1:56:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直把我帶在身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:39.03,1:56:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我感謝您
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.38,1:56:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從心底
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.71,1:56:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}教會了我用心去愛人
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.75,1:57:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感謝您
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.03,1:57:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您對我說的那句我愛妳
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.59,1:57:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我活下去的指路明燈
Dialogue: 0,1:57:15.78,1:57:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當我知道什麼是愛後
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.69,1:57:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我便想向您說我愛您
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.39,1:57:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.67,1:57:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.32,1:57:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直以來
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.68,1:57:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的非常感謝您」
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.44,1:58:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人啊 都不會輕易透露內心啊
Dialogue: 0,1:58:39.27,1:58:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}布甘比利亞家由我來繼承
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.60,1:58:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你儘管走自己的路
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.76,1:58:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去啊
Dialogue: 0,2:00:14.26,2:00:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.59,2:00:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特！
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.92,2:00:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校
Dialogue: 0,2:00:39.35,2:00:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吉爾伯特
Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.00,2:01:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校
Dialogue: 0,2:01:05.62,2:01:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.82,2:02:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少校
Dialogue: 0,2:02:12.34,2:02:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,2:02:14.16,2:02:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已經不是妳的主人或長官了
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.14,2:02:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我傷害了妳
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.10,2:02:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是妳想像中那麼好的男人
Dialogue: 0,2:02:31.17,2:02:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是一個好主人 更不是一個好人
Dialogue: 0,2:02:39.46,2:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定配不上妳
Dialogue: 0,2:02:51.42,2:02:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但要是
Dialogue: 0,2:03:01.20,2:03:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在我還是
Dialogue: 0,2:03:07.35,2:03:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛著妳
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.66,2:03:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…
Dialogue: 0,2:03:19.69,2:03:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}待在我身邊 薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,2:03:27.91,2:03:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.45,2:03:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少…
Dialogue: 0,2:03:41.66,2:03:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少…
Dialogue: 0,2:03:44.76,2:03:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…
Comment: 0,2:03:47.77,2:03:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…
Dialogue: 0,2:03:52.94,2:03:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特 不要哭
Dialogue: 0,2:03:58.42,2:04:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妳看我 也要快哭了
Dialogue: 0,2:04:06.98,2:04:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想幫妳擦眼淚
Dialogue: 0,2:04:11.57,2:04:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜託了 把頭抬起來
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.46,2:04:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…
Dialogue: 0,2:04:25.14,2:04:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對少校您…
Dialogue: 0,2:04:33.42,2:04:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對少校您…
Dialogue: 0,2:05:03.66,2:05:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我愛妳 薇爾莉特
Dialogue: 0,2:05:09.74,2:05:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直想這麼抱著妳
Dialogue: 0,2:08:53.30,2:08:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她把手頭上的工作全部完成後
Dialogue: 0,2:08:58.31,2:09:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}便辭掉了現在郵局的工作
Dialogue: 0,2:09:02.73,2:09:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後接過了小島燈塔的郵政業務
Dialogue: 0,2:09:08.99,2:09:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在這個郵局
Dialogue: 0,2:09:10.37,2:09:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}似乎已經搬到鎮裡的道路邊了
Dialogue: 0,2:09:31.42,2:09:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然電話開始普及 人偶這份職業開始被淘汰
Dialogue: 0,2:09:38.92,2:09:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但估計她在這裡
Dialogue: 0,2:09:42.48,2:09:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是幫大家代筆過許多信件吧
Dialogue: 0,2:09:52.75,2:09:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不然
Dialogue: 0,2:09:57.35,2:09:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這枚郵票啊
Dialogue: 0,2:09:59.41,2:10:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是CH郵局紀念財團只在這座島發行的郵票
Dialogue: 0,2:10:06.97,2:10:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這座小島有個人 一年內寄出的信件是全國最多的
Dialogue: 0,2:10:14.37,2:10:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前有個叫人偶的職業
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.00,2:10:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這座小島也有一個大家都喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,2:10:22.29,2:10:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常有人氣的人偶住在這裡
Dialogue: 0,2:10:33.02,2:10:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}名字叫
Dialogue: 0,2:10:34.80,2:10:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}薇爾莉特·伊芙嘉登
Dialogue: 0,2:10:41.89,2:10:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的外太婆
Dialogue: 0,2:10:43.59,2:10:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也曾經讓她幫忙寫過信
Dialogue: 0,2:11:03.12,2:11:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}言語說不出來
Dialogue: 0,2:11:05.90,2:11:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或許能表達在信裡
Dialogue: 0,2:11:11.13,2:11:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也想表達最真摯的感情
Dialogue: 0,2:11:16.45,2:11:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的收信人
Dialogue: 0,2:11:20.99,2:11:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有現在才能收到你的信
Dialogue: 0,2:11:40.72,2:11:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,2:11:44.22,2:11:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,2:11:50.34,2:11:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你們
